Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听比拿可说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了人体链成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你回来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经没有你的立身之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么烧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我决定了不再回头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示我们的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想再看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃避不堪回首的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想掩盖自己所犯下的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和晚上尿床的小孩把床单藏起来是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃避了 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我年轻的时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}墓前的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和以前完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉夏一直在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子们链成的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是朵莉夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有形成人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能说是朵莉夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 眼睛的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说那不是朵莉夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制作完全无关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子失去了身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用吃饭睡觉 一直能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要这个印记完好无损的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是不老不死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是装了个不定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴利说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来不同人之间的灵魂和肉体是无法相容的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬是放到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会产生拒绝反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是明天还是10年后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不马上恢复原来的身体就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果觉得身体不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把灵魂转移到别的东西上继续生存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使维持现状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感受不到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不需要食物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个身体不是很方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次都是哥哥或者温莉先生气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都没机会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这个身体无法睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够恢复原来的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还回来 我弟弟的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把弟弟变成那种身体的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不要这种身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拿走这张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人一起照的只有这张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为回礼 告诉你一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家马上要发生很糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃去别的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的事情又不少见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些小家伙把这里当作归宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说我没忠告过你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也回来吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 比拿可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计再也吃不到你做的饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要把那个挖出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要停手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手脚的衔接处在痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下雨了 快点做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确认的话就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 妈妈的头发是棕色才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿骨 太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男人的骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 死去的人无法复生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始 这就是绝望的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在却和希望相连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔能取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是卡迪斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是爱德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想问师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 给我说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是师傅进行人体链成的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阿尔链成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 你到底想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅链成的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是师傅的小孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子们在战场上好好干了一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 他什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个重要的口信要给他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口信？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朵莉夏的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个人回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我告诉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定？是什么约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 如果遇到那家伙替我转告他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看他那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是很关心你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍他一拳之后我再转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回中央都市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去被阿尔臭駡一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一个人干了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然坏成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人 刽子手巴利？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有无法相容的身体和灵魂之间的拒绝反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剩下的铠甲拉长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔能取回原来的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了能恢复就能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在利塞布尔 我把那时我们链成的东西挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从结果来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明了那个不是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们链成了完全不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我获得了能取回你身体的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谈这个话题之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温…温莉 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否记得我们兄弟俩因为谁要娶你而吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在屋顶上说过的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你把阿尔甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 甩了 甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有事要问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甩了他的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要比我身高还低的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用身高决定男人的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这和阿尔的身体有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 阿尔知道我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的事情温莉也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说那是真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为记得真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以固定在铠甲上的是真正的阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那扇门里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是把你成功地拉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果灵魂能拉出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也应该能把肉体从门里拉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和灵魂分离 并且肉体还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刽子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拉进真理之中的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和灵魂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把肉体也拉出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从被认为是妈妈的那个东西里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里面的 原来是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是因为拒绝反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂没有固定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我们没有伤害任何人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹米·卡迪斯小姐打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了我的家谱和丈夫的家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链成出来的孩子的肤色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我们夫妇之间无法产生的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查到什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复阿尔身体的信心和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死去的人复生是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是缺少什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是做不到的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了“谢谢”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始就一直在责备自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妈妈变成那种样子的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有杀死妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有第二次杀死那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我把你的身体变成了那样是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么 我都要把你的身体恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞同了那种做法的我也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老是满口自己一个人来背负的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么都自己一个人背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再因为自己的事情而让别人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯先生也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当知道他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想 如果要牺牲别人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不恢复身体也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看过许多 即使有着不是人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以自己的风格活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这种身体 周围的人也把我当人一样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活生生的身体也一样会有预料不到的生老病死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想普通地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体也没有任何不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能这样想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再度过独自一人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恢复身体的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我们干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢飞真理那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把你的身体拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的背影有那么高大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤同伴的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使男人的步伐加速
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年为了走出死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加了乾坤一掷的胜败
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21话 愚者的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的帷幕由自己拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:06.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:37.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:43.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:44.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:49.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:08.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:22.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:27.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
